---
import { FaUserTie, FaQuoteLeft, FaBriefcase, FaGraduationCap } from 'react-icons/fa';
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-gray-100">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">
      About Dr. Hon. Antony Manyara
    </h2>

<!-- Bio Section -->
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg text-center mb-12">
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
    Hon. Antony Manyara was raised in Meru County, Kenya. He has been involved in leadership from a young age, serving as a youth leader in several organizations across Kenya and Africa. Manyara was the chairperson of University of Nairobi Students Association (UNSA - formerly SONU) in 2018/2019, Kenya University Students Organization (KUSO) chairperson since 2020, and Kenya's representative in the Commonwealth Youth Council in 2021/2022. Manyara was appointed by Moussa Faki, former AU chairperson, as a youth leader in the Africa Progress Group. Since 2024, Manyara has been serving as an ambassador of sustainable housing with Kenya's Ministry of Housing. A firm believer in the power of the people, he is committed to ensuring the voice of the common mwananchi is heard.
  </p>
</div>


    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
        <!-- Role 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-center">
          <FaUserTie class="w-10 h-10 text-indigo-600 mx-auto mb-4" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">President</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Kenya University Students Organization (KUSO)</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Role 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-center">
          <FaBriefcase class="w-10 h-10 text-indigo-600 mx-auto mb-4" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">CEO</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Youth Advocacy Africa (YAA)</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Role 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-center">
          <FaGraduationCap class="w-10 h-10 text-indigo-600 mx-auto mb-4" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">Education</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">BArch Studies, University of Nairobi | Honorary Doctorate, Weldios University</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-700 text-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Core Values</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="font-semibold">Integrity</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="font-semibold">Hard Work</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="font-semibold">Empowerment</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

